column5: I appreciate your videos so much. I’ve saved some in the past for times when I especially need to hear it. So thank you! You’re a wonderful person!
This looks awesome! I understand being worried what others may think or say, but you honestly are talented!

Hatsumi is a new Japanese place on fremont that’s amazing! Other mama is off the strip, and nowhere near fremont, and it’s excellent also! They’re known for their oysters, and fun play on other seafood cuisine! Have fun!
